text: Krang Thnong Commune () is a khum (commune) in Bati District, Takéo Province, Cambodia. == Administration == As of 2019, Krang Thnong Commune has 8 phums (villages) as follows. {| class="wikitable sortable mw-collapsible" !No. !Code !Village !Khmer |- !1 |21020701 |Haknuman |ហនុមាន |- !2 |21020702 |Tbaeng |ត្បែង |- !3 |21020703 |Khnar |ខ្នារ |- !4 |21020704 |Thnal Teaksen |ថ្នល់ទក្សិណ |- !5 |21020705 |Chroung Sdau |ជ្រោងស្ដៅ |- !6 |21020706 |Tboung Damrei |ត្បូងដំរី |- !7 |21020707 |Krang Thnong |ក្រាំងធ្នង់ |- !8 |21020708 |Tonle Bati |ទន្លេបាទី |} == References == Category:Communes of Takeo Province Category:Bati District
